   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>I, Aphrodeisios, owe to Melli 1400 drachmai. Of these, I have paid off to Mellis 380 drachmai, to be taken from Doulos, and 200 drachmai from Moros the priets; and for Arok the herdsman(?), 480 drachmai; Pannous, 340 drachmai. And Mellis himself (has?) 1 artabe of barley.</ab>
